### Variables
@apiVersion = /api/admin

###
### ============================================
### DOCTOR ENDPOINTS - LIST DOCTORS
### ============================================
###

### List Doctors - Success (Super Admin or Admin)
# @name listDoctors
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/doctors
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Doctors - Without Authentication
# Should return 401 Unauthorized
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/doctors
Accept: application/json

### List Doctors - Unauthorized (Secretary Role)
# Should return 403 Forbidden
# Note: Requires a token from a user with secretary role
GET {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/doctors
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{secretaryToken}}

